Package: R.MFIV
Title: Calculate Model Free Implied Volatility, i.e. the CBOE VIX from Option Quotes
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Martin Georg",
           family = "Haas",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "haasmartin@live.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0977-0939"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate the CBOE VIX, intermediary values and the Jiang & Tian (2007)<doi:doi.org/10.3905/jod.2007.68181310.3905/jod.2007.681813> smoothing method to deal with an insufficient strike price range.
